27:["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-5 text-sm leading-7 text-muted-foreground","children":["\"","I met Dr. Vaijayanti at Dr. Anita Soni clinic when I conceived in 2025. She has been a blessing in disguise as when you are becoming a first time parent your life is full of doubts, fears and what not, and Dr. Vaijayanti never got tired from thousands of my questions. She guided the best way possible. Amazing doctor I must say.","\""]}]
