2a:["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-5 text-sm leading-7 text-muted-foreground","children":["\"","Dr. Vaijayanti is a very caring and good doctor. She listens to her patients carefully and gives them good treatment. She explains things clearly and is very kind. I had a great experience with her, and I really appreciate how she makes her patients feel comfortable. Love u Mam.","\""]}]
